trans-unit.source: Exposes <see cref="T:System.Windows.UIElement3D" /> types to UI Automation.
trans-unit.target: Expõe tipos <see cref="T:System.Windows.UIElement3D" /> à Automação de Interface do Usuário.

trans-unit.source: By default, any class that inherits from <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> uses <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer> to communicate with [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Por padrão, qualquer classe que herda <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> usa <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer> para se comunicar com [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: If you create a class that inherits from <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D>, you may want to provide an automation peer to support the functionality of your class.
trans-unit.target: Se você criar uma classe que herda de <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D>, talvez seja necessário fornecer um par de automação para oferecer suporte à funcionalidade de sua classe.

trans-unit.source: Override the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetClassNameCore%2A> method to return a string that represents the type of the element associated with the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer>.
trans-unit.target: Substituir o <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetClassNameCore%2A> método para retornar uma cadeia de caracteres que representa o tipo do elemento associado a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer>.

trans-unit.source: For example, if you create a class called `My3DElement` and an automation peer called `My3DElementAutomationPeer`, override the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetClassNameCore%2A> method to return the string "My3DElement".
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, se você criar uma classe chamada `My3DElement` e um par de automação chamada `My3DElementAutomationPeer`, substituir o <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetClassNameCore%2A> método para retornar a cadeia de caracteres "My3DElement".

trans-unit.source: If your class matches one of the known control types, override the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetAutomationControlTypeCore%2A> method to return that <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType>.
trans-unit.target: Se sua classe corresponde a um dos tipos de controle conhecidos, substituir o <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetAutomationControlTypeCore%2A> método para retornar que <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType>.

trans-unit.source: Note that although the existing <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType> values are generally associated with 2D controls, the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType> indicates a control's functionality, not its appearance.
trans-unit.target: Observe que embora existente <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType> valores são geralmente associados a controles 2D, o <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType> indica a funcionalidade de um controle, não sua aparência.

trans-unit.source: So if your <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> invokes an action when the user clicks it, you probably want <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetHelpTextCore%2A> to return <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: Portanto, se seu <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> invoca uma ação quando o usuário clica, provavelmente você desejará <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetHelpTextCore%2A> para retornar <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType>.

trans-unit.source: The behavior of your custom <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> determines what other methods you should override.
trans-unit.target: O comportamento de personalizados <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> determina quais outros métodos que você deve substituir.
